240
00:17:03,030 --> 00:17:04,790
Awak menonjol ke mana saja awak pergi.

241
00:17:06,109 --> 00:17:09,060
Awak nampak saya begitu?
Saya bersinar terang macam berlian?

242
00:17:10,119 --> 00:17:12,230
Maknanya awak boleh cari saya
